{
  "id": "adv_event_2502_01_03",
  "title": "とろける\nような青春",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二月十四日バレンタインデー当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—February 14th‚ Valentine’s Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3332221
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、遙子さん\nお疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ Haruko-san.\nThank you for your hard work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5333332221,
      "endTime": 5.4769386928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、大きな紙袋を両手一杯に抱えてどうしたの？\nもしかして……それ全部、バレンタインのチョコ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ what’s with that big paper bag you’re holding with both arms?\nCould it be… those are all Valentine chocolates?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6836052736,
      "endTime": 17.5959177812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "学校帰りに校門の前で後輩の子達に囲まれて、次々に\nチョコを渡されたんです。人数が多くて大変でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On my way home from school‚ I was surrounded by underclassmen at the school gate‚\nand they kept handing me chocolates one after another. There were so many‚ it was tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7892518203,
      "endTime": 28.165260617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "女子校は美人で格好いい先輩が人気があるって言うよな\n怜は後輩達にとって憧れの格好いい先輩ってことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say at girls’ schools‚ pretty and cool seniors are really popular.\nSo to your juniors‚ Rei‚ you’re that admired‚ cool senior.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3519273599,
      "endTime": 38.36097517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしいから、あんまり茶化さないで下さい\nそれより、さくら達はまだ来てないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s embarrassing‚ so please don’t tease me too much.\nMore importantly‚ have Sakura and the others not arrived yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5011332672,
      "endTime": 45.9477091949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら達ならまだ学校のはずだ\nとりあえず全員揃うまでお茶でも飲んで待っていてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura and the others should still be at school.\nFor now‚ have some tea and wait until everyone’s here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1343757471,
      "endTime": 52.826144679500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、美味しいケーキを買ってあるんだ。俺と\nたわいもない世間話でもしながら一緒に食べないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right—I bought some delicious cake.\nHow about we eat together while chatting about nothing in particular?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.032811308,
      "endTime": 60.755510552400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとうございます……\n急にケーキなんて、どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ thank you very much…\nWhat’s with the sudden cake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9761221092,
      "endTime": 68.1775279204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "別に他意はないよ。なんとなく今日はみんなと\nお喋りしたい気分なんだ。本当にそれだけだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no ulterior motive. I just kind of feel like\nchatting with everyone today. That’s really all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2,
      "endTime": 75.91759257289999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、今日はバレンタインかー。好きな人に\nチョコを贈る日かー。みんなはどうするのかなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ it’s Valentine’s Day today— The day you give chocolates\nto someone you like— I wonder what everyone’s going to do—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.116548745,
      "endTime": 87.3669340294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。ねぇ、もしかして、私達が誰にチョコを\n渡すのか気になって、探りを入れてるのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu. Hey‚ could it be that you’re trying to\nsneakily find out who we’re giving chocolates to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5936047078,
      "endTime": 96.6121342342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、別に、みんなが誰に本命チョコをあげるのか\n気になってるとかそんなんじゃ全然なくて……全然……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not at all—it’s not like I’m curious about\nwho everyone’s giving their true feeling chocolate to… not at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8177769821,
      "endTime": 104.1930157974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁぁぁぁぁ……すみません、物凄く気になってます\n変な人に騙されていないか、気が気じゃなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaah… sorry‚ I’m honestly way too curious.\nI just can’t stop worrying that you might be getting fooled by some weird person…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2666707356,
      "endTime": 115.4436961009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、心配性な保護者みたいね\n大丈夫よ。相手はちゃんとした人だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun‚ you sound like an overprotective guardian.\nIt’s fine. The person is a proper‚ reliable one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6837407272,
      "endTime": 124.0011328857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、遙子さんはみんなが誰に本命チョコを\n渡すか知っているんですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you really do know who everyone’s giving\ntheir true feeling chocolates to‚ Haruko-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.187799724,
      "endTime": 129.0333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛をするなとは言いません。ただ、アイドルに\n恋人がいるなんて噂になったら大事ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not saying you can’t have romances. But if rumors start\nabout idols having lovers‚ it can become a big issue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2557589372,
      "endTime": 135.6666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "事務所としても、マネージャーとしても、備えだけは\nしておきたいんです。だから教えてもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As an agency‚ and as a manager‚\nI want to be prepared. So could you tell me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9053731442,
      "endTime": 143.6926299882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。今は教える訳にはいかないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry. I can’t tell you right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8937628588,
      "endTime": 148.10909159989998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……分かりました……。ああ、でも気になる\nみんなが本命チョコを渡す相手は一体どんな人なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… understood… Aah‚ but I can’t help wondering.\nWhat kind of person is everyone giving their true feeling chocolates to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3024248761,
      "endTime": 158.6345798802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "本当に気付いてないんですね……。ところで、そこの\n段ボール箱の山はファンから届いたチョコですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really haven’t noticed‚ have you… By the way‚\nthose stacks of cardboard boxes are chocolates from fans‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8229235015,
      "endTime": 168.7995449386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "この量を抱えて帰るのはさすがに無理なので\nイベントが終わった後に寮まで運んでもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Carrying all that home would be impossible‚\nso could you bring them to the dorm after the event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.012878005,
      "endTime": 176.61432921120002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "イベントまで日にちがあるし\n別に今日運んでも構わないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s still time before the event‚\nso I wouldn’t mind moving them today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.8209960304,
      "endTime": 182.48503230440002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、イベントの後でお願いします\nその日なら、みんなも寮にいるはずなので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ please do it after the event.\nEveryone should be at the dorm that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.6983625097,
      "endTime": 189.35654827780002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、必ず{user}君が\n寮に持って来てね。みんなで待ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right—make sure you\nbring them to the dorm‚ {user}-kun. We’ll all be waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.5498816492,
      "endTime": 196.2928524019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――放課後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After school",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.1728545508,
      "endTime": 198.2061878842,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6687012000011
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.2061878842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ～！　遅くなってごめんね\n教室を出る時にいろいろあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you waiting~! I’m late!\nA lot happened when I was leaving the classroom…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.039523252,
      "endTime": 205.3885254225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.5751920702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
